## Limitations

The analysis is based on information available up to October 2023, and the situation may have evolved since then. Additionally, while the sources used are credible, there may be other factors contributing to the shortage that were not covered in the available literature. The focus was primarily on the U.S. market, and the situation may differ in other regions.